name: OutpatientPrenatalVisit
title: Outpatient Prenatal Visit
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for encounters where a pregnant patient would be seen by a clinician for routine prenatal care in the outpatient setting.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Encounter.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that represent an encounter with OB/GYN specialty physicians for pregnant patients without or with complications in the outpatient setting.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
